data.description: You must see this beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom 2 story home located in Barbers Hill ISD. As you walk in the front door you will be greeted by a large family room that opens up to a sizable dining area and a chef ready kitchen perfect for entertaining. Upstairs you will find a master retreat complete with a spacious walk-in closet & 2 secondary bedrooms. This home also features energy efficient appliances, upgraded wood cabinets, and brushed nickel hardware. Call today to schedule your private showing to make this home your home sweet home!
